__NOTOC__
{{Server client function}}
{{New feature/item|3.0160|1.5.8|20788|Determines whether or not the transferbox should appear to [[Player|players]].}}

==Syntax==
<syntaxhighlight lang="lua">
bool setTransferBoxVisible ( bool visible )
</syntaxhighlight>

===Required Arguments=== 
*'''visible:''' The new visibility state.

===Returns===
Returns ''true'' if the visibility was set successfully, ''false'' otherwise.

==Examples==

<section name="Server" class="server" show="true">
<syntaxhighlight lang="lua">
addEventHandler('onResourceStart', resourceRoot, function()
    setTransferBoxVisible(false)
end)
</syntaxhighlight>
</section>

==Requirements==
{{Requirements|1.5.8-9.20788|1.5.8-9.20788|}}

